casebody.data:
No. 10-6739. Ernest Miller, Petitioner v. California. 562 U.S. 1057, 131 S. Ct. 662,

178 L. Ed. 2d 473,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9054. November 29, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied, and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the Supreme Court of California dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
